block assignment
  p
    | Now it's time to put what you've learned to the test (pun intended). Clone both repos below in to your Cloud9 workspace and see if you can get some of the tests fixed. 
  ul
    li create c9 account
    li create new project by cloning the <a href="https://github.com/liammclennan/JavaScript-Koans.git">jskoans repository</a>
    li make the following tests pass:
      ul
        li assert
        li operators
        li equality
    li create a new project by cloning <a href="https://github.com/rmurphey/js-assessment.git">the js-assessment repository</a>
    li use command line to install modules
    li update node-port-path
    li start node
    li view in sidebar (or new tab)
    li assert a test